casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Solowitch.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Solowitch (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 155.]

(No. 91-2090 Submitted November 5, 1991 Decided November 13, 1991.)

The resignation of Eric Steven Solowitch as an attorney, Registration No. 0000472, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
